Using names like this might make sense

35
00:01:36,220 --> 00:01:39,810
if it's mostly a static class full of utility methods

36
00:01:39,810 --> 00:01:41,150
or anything like that,

37
00:01:41,150 --> 00:01:43,540
but typically, you wanna avoid them

38
